Invocation Name: mythical creature personality quiz
des: Have you ever daydreamed about being a mermaid lounging in the sea? Or being a fire-breathing dragon to vanquish your enemies? Perhaps you're more in tune with a mythical creature than you know! Take this fun quiz to see if your personality is more in tune with a mythical creature rather than your human form.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
